{"tid":2137290,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗：冠軍獻予抗疫鬥士","createTime":"2020-08-02T23:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T09:12:27.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff773ba46ced9003bdf846fb0996a2c98e56403","tid":2137290,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:13:55.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】基斯坦奴朗拿度在周日帶領祖雲達斯成就意甲9連霸，賽後表示把冠軍獻給所有遭受新型冠狀病毒疫情折磨的人。<br />\n<br />\n「完成！我們是意大利冠軍！」前鋒基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）賽後於Instagram寫道。「我很高興能夠連續第2季捧走聯賽，繼續為這偉大且輝煌的球會寫下歷史。」 雖然球季一度因為新型冠狀病毒而停擺，但祖雲達斯在重啟後仍然可以保持領先優勢。C朗表示：「我要把這個錦標獻給所有祖記球迷，特別是那些遭受疫情折磨的人。」 另外，祖雲達斯首席足球官柏拉迪斯承認，正跟C朗拍檔迪巴拿傾續約：「我們經常和他身邊的人傾談，儘管每3天便有1場比賽，令我們難以作出甚麼行動及承諾，但這場談判的進度很好，已進入另一階段。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做乜9有意甲都唔要，正一傻閪朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4ca2f19b901e755e47cf02a475367df23a9f51","tid":2137290,"uid":45498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:14:19.000Z","msg":"佢點獻的"},{"pid":"6a31e8cf2e18ba2a48e4a68ee6ef484e15c65755","tid":2137290,"uid":287534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:14:28.000Z","msg":"你點獻的"},{"pid":"90745582a49a711eaa4ab45ae72a5fd608d9766c","tid":2137290,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:15:55.000Z","msg":"他點獻的"},{"pid":"d0e874e3e5a05a100cfa531f179a765e1b888e35","tid":2137290,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:20:10.000Z","msg":"他知道"},{"pid":"3b1f1646316941bcdb14e992b5e03399a61f6058","tid":2137290,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:35:35.000Z","msg":"佢點獻的"},{"pid":"738738b3c3adf7fe95938b711879ce9469582da2","tid":2137290,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.g